{"tid":1890422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民號召獻花撐確診警員　無人出席","createTime":"2020-02-21T07:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T08:08:06.000Z","uid":36494,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f28b888f573540036369693b02d41c55fdc48058","tid":1890422,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"本港昨新增3宗新型冠狀病毒確診，當中首度有警員染病。事件曝光後，有網民發起撐警活動，號召撐警的人今明（21、22日）中午到聯合醫院大堂獻花，支持確診的警員。本報今早到聯合醫院守候，至下午近2時，只有醫護人員和一些病人家屬出現，未見有任何撐警者到場獻花。<br />\n<br />\n針對相關活動，醫管局今早發聲明，表示公立醫院已啟動緊急應變級別，全面禁止探訪，基於公眾衛生考慮，呼籲市民不應前往公立醫院聚集，以免引起散播傳染病的風險。"},{"pid":"cdf967b4ca80bca655d4acce205f9bcd072ca38c","tid":1890422,"uid":6141,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"去墳前獻啦"},{"pid":"55113f90044e7cbafda92bea62910389cd1edbad","tid":1890422,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:05:08.000Z","msg":"柒<br />\n今時今日仲撐警係咪未俾差佬扑過"},{"pid":"e4b9ef16fc5120ed0fadc0d7a8e1ab93d464cf96","tid":1890422,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"有咩留番拜山講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52d85b27dd46af87789981395c0fbec9ef42f46","tid":1890422,"uid":270390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf967b4ca80bca655d4acce205f9bcd072ca38c","tid":1890422,"uid":6141,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"去墳前獻啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ede52ce64f6a93b1e2c34b2c4a398451f2f5951","tid":1890422,"uid":215270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:07:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji